name: koolklawz
review: This is my second time purchasing this eyeliner in black, and I plan to buy it in all the colors. I saw it the first time while out shopping, and what drew my attention was that the packaging stated it was waterline-safe. I'm generally a liquid or gel liner wearer, but have been playing with bolder looks. I love the initial shape of this liner, but it dulls pretty quickly. It still gets the job done, but I'd love to be able to maintain its flat edge for thinner lines. This liner is so smooth it glides on like a gel. It's ultra-black and perfect for the waterline and tightlining. It's very soft, so I have to be careful not to use so much pressure it clumps in my lashes. On the flip side, its softness makes it great for smudging out, and the soft brush on the other end is great for blending it out.

name: Pat
review: I purchased the evergreen color which I love against my blue eyes. This color looks good with just mascara. I love the angled pencil. It makes applying so much easier. I plan to get another color I like it so much.

name: Mari
review: It's a great color, amazing price, and blends easily.  I only wish there were some way to sharpen it back to the original shape.  Sometimes I'd like a crisper line.

name: Lisaland2017
review: LOVE ❤️ THIS PRODUCT. No eyeliner stays in place (no transferring to beneath eyes whatsoever) like this one does. I received 3-4 compliments from diff co-workers first couple times I wore it. Makes eyes pop beautifully.

name: LMKAMINSK
review: Love this. Very easy to use. Stays put. Smokes out easily.  Feels like it doesn't irritate eyes as much as wax based products. I really like the fact that the brown color has a purplish tinge.  The smudge brush is super soft.

name: Shelby
review: In the past I have always used a dark eyeshadow applied with a small brush in place of eyeliner. But this is even better because the eyeliner stays in place better than a shadow but I can still soften it with the brush. I originally just had this at work for when I didn't have time to do all of my makeup at home, but now I use it all the time. I have two colors and I'm buying a third one in my next Ulta order.

name: Young grandma
review: Love the angled tip. You can go with a thick or thin line or use the brush end to go smokie.
